{"tid":365972,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何 紫 綸 摸 外 籍 肌 男 心 跳 加 速","createTime":"2017-08-19T16:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T05:44:18.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"640ba165669eb6d297a6728f3f09d19582afe781","tid":365972,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:03:10.000Z","msg":"女子組合星座少女Staries噚日喺老闆何紫綸（右三）見證下，擔任尖沙嘴一間健身中心代言人，四人跟老闆娘輕摸半裸外籍俊男肌肉合照，誰不知人妻何紫綸臉紅怕醜，佢事後解釋有一段時間未摸過胸肌，只係摸一大嚿腹肌，所以心跳加速，何紫綸仲話：「老公結咗婚之後就貨不對辦，都要畀啲鼓勵佢去操吓。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170815/large/15ec5p20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170815%2Flarge%2F15ec5p20.jpg&h=d7bd611e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45d021f790eabd53fd13737d8496ec4e637bcfc7","tid":365972,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"d047300a13dc79fa6374671b5239745ebf7dff1a","tid":365972,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aefef99c43dd783e79f630fcc78c23c6900b96ad","tid":365972,"uid":4874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>g</blockquote>"}]}